This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3575

| <- Represents the cursor

# body { | }

In the above situation, pressing enter, the result is as follows

# body {
        |
}

Other examples

<tr>|</tr>

<tr>
        |
</tr>

{if} | {endif}

{if}
        |
{endif}

github: http://github.com/acustodioo/vim-enter-indent
My vimrc with this and other plugins: http://github.com/acustodioo/dotfiles

